# Copernicus Marine credentials template
# ----------------------------------------
# 1. Copy this file and rename it:
#       cp .example_.copernicusmarine-credentials .copernicusmarine-credentials
#
# 2. Base64-encode your credentials and paste the result as the file content.
#    Run the following command, replacing the username and password:
#
#       printf '[credentials]\nusername=YOUR_USERNAME\npassword=YOUR_PASSWORD' | base64
#
# 3. The final .copernicusmarine-credentials file should contain only the
#    base64-encoded string, for example:
#
#       W2NyZWRlbnRpYWxzXQ0KdXNlcm5hbWU9eW91cnVzZXJuYW1lDQpwYXNzd29yZD15b3VycGFzc3dvcmQ=
#